info: Rating, 5 stars,  路 June 2023,  路 Stayed one night
rating_comment:
Guests should understand that this is a Motel like place. Single Studio apartments. It has reception on the front, parking, and is staffed 24 hours. Single Elevator. Building has some new construction ongoing. Paint and chemical smell is present and can be felt through the Closed-Door and AC.
The staffs are professional, however, need to be more proactive; offer assistance.
